            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "The car theft crime wave continues, only it’s becoming increasingly common for criminals to just carjack people instead of boosting their rides when they’re parked. At about 4 am on May 18 a robbery suspect picked the wrong guy to carjack. The owner of a C8 Corvette felt his life was in danger, so he pulled out a gun and shot the suspect several times. That person then jumped on a car which was driving away, but fell off it and died in the parking lot.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
